<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716289939955086858.png" title="1716289939955086858.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-21 191158.png" width="734" height="365" style="width: 734px; height: 365px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716289969458017348.png" style="width: 739px; height: 412px;" title="1716289969458017348.png" width="739" height="412"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240521/1716289970239063153.png" style="" title="1716289970239063153.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px;">为扎实有效推进基层党建工作，4月1日上午，学校党委在我院</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">A10-314</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px;">党员活动室召开4月党群部门负责人、党总支书记工作例会。党委领导班子成员、各党群部门负责人、各党总支书记参加会议。会议由校党委书记、督导专员江延湖主持。</span><br/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">议程一：汇报特色亮点工作</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">首先，会议听取了经济管理学院党总支书记蔡平关于特色亮点工作的汇报。蔡平书记围绕“踏踏实实做事、做真事、做实事”的工作理念对学院的党建工作、学工工作、志愿活动等方面展开分享。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">随后，新媒体学院党总支书记王芳介绍了新媒体学院的“1131”学生工作机制，其内容包括“1个中心、1个机制、3个关口、1个防线”的特色亮点工作，为学校学生工作的创新提供了新思路。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">议程二：各党总支书记工作汇报</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">接着，各学院党总支书记针对3月已开展的党员发展、党员教育管理、学生活动、学生工作管理、安全教育、就业工作等方面工作进行了深入交流和探讨，并对4月份计划开展的工作进行了汇报。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">议程三：各党群负责人部署相关工作</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">接着，团委、学工处、宣传部、统战部、组织部、教师工作部等部门负责人分别就4月工作作出部署安排，其主要涵盖赛事、辅导员管理、师生宗教信仰摸排、党员教育发展、师德师风等方面内容。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">议程四：校党委书记、督导专员江延湖讲话</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">最后，校党委书记、督导专员江延湖在总结讲话中对各级党组织取得的阶段性成绩给予充分肯定，并指出学院基层党建工作中存在的问题和不足，同时对下一步开展工作提出四点要求：一是“善学习”，注意把握学习重点，积极拓展学习平台，坚持自主学习与集中学习相结合，理论学习与业务相结合，切实增强学习效果；二是“守底线”，提出安全问题和防诈骗的重要性，要全方位保证校园稳定安全；三是“树亮点”，要持续开展创建各学院品牌工作，进一步打造各学院工作特色亮点，思考并推进“一院一品牌”建设；四是“抓日常”，通过结合各学院的日常工作例会，将工作落实到实处，形成日常工作常态化和制度化。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">此次党群部门负责人、党总支书记工作例会的召开，不仅为各学院党总支之间的交流与合作搭建了平台，更进一步深化院校融合，促进共同发展；同时，也为我院4月份即将开展的工作指明了方向。在校党委的正确领导下，我院将以更扎实有效的举措推动学院各项工作高质量发展。</span></p>